isDeleteDisabled

public boolean isDeleteDisabled()
Determines whether the delete button is disabled. The delete button should be disabled if the node that was previously selected was deleted or if no node is otherwise selected. The root node is a special case and cannot be deleted.

Returns:
the disabled status of the delete button
